1
00:00:00,424 --> 00:00:08,524
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,699 --> 00:00:16,936
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,174 --> 00:00:19,165
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,179 --> 00:00:25,945
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,016 --> 00:00:29,383
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,586 --> 00:00:33,147
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,523 --> 00:00:36,890
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:44,389
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,468 --> 00:00:53,604
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,677 --> 00:01:01,709
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:01,952 --> 00:01:08,790
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,859 --> 00:01:16,925
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,234 --> 00:01:25,699
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,776 --> 00:01:27,801
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:50,578 --> 00:01:52,307
Tomorrow, huh...

16
00:01:53,314 --> 00:01:59,310
<i>The Final Rounds.</i>
<i>Rush to the Battle Arena!</i>

17
00:02:11,599 --> 00:02:13,897
What's up? It's been a while.

18
00:02:15,069 --> 00:02:17,867
Heh heh...
I was kind of in the hospital.

19
00:02:17,938 --> 00:02:18,927
The hospital?

20
00:02:19,006 --> 00:02:21,304
I'm totally fine, now.

21
00:02:21,375 --> 00:02:23,366
Nothing to it!

22
00:02:24,378 --> 00:02:25,572
I see.

23
00:02:27,982 --> 00:02:28,676
Ayame!

24
00:02:28,749 --> 00:02:29,374
Yes!

25
00:02:31,118 --> 00:02:32,847
Here you go.

26
00:02:40,961 --> 00:02:41,950
Pops?

27
00:02:42,463 --> 00:02:43,760
Just eat it.

28
00:02:44,365 --> 00:02:46,230
The final round is tomorrow, right?

29
00:02:52,139 --> 00:02:53,071
Okay, then.

30
00:02:53,974 --> 00:02:55,839
Thanks!

31
00:03:02,049 --> 00:03:05,143
You've got a daughter at home,
so it's not so bad, right?

32
00:03:05,786 --> 00:03:08,516
Most of my money vanishes
with the food expenses.

33
00:03:08,856 --> 00:03:12,223
Moron. Your home is special, right?

34
00:03:12,393 --> 00:03:13,189
Huh?

35
00:03:13,494 --> 00:03:15,962
Girls are a drag.

36
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:21,332
Yeah. There are times when I really
don't get how to act with her.

37
00:03:21,535 --> 00:03:24,402
Father's have it rough...

38
00:03:24,938 --> 00:03:27,372
Hah, am I the only bad guy?

39
00:03:28,509 --> 00:03:30,136
Hey, master.

40
00:03:30,511 --> 00:03:34,038
Let me have everything
on these two pages, too!

41
00:03:34,181 --> 00:03:35,239
Welcome!

42
00:03:37,751 --> 00:03:40,481
Oh! Strong reinforcements!

43
00:03:40,554 --> 00:03:42,283
Come on. You order something, too!

44
00:03:46,427 --> 00:03:48,258
Hey... Dad.

45
00:03:48,328 --> 00:03:49,659
Hmm?

46
00:03:49,730 --> 00:03:51,891
Hey! Let's go home, already!

47
00:03:52,132 --> 00:03:53,326
Excuse me?

48
00:03:53,767 --> 00:03:58,500
Shut up. You're supposed to
live it up at a festival!

49
00:03:58,839 --> 00:04:00,773
Festival, my butt...

50
00:04:02,042 --> 00:04:03,509
What a drag.

51
00:04:03,644 --> 00:04:06,636
You idiot... Since olden times...

52
00:04:11,819 --> 00:04:15,448
the final round's
been like a festival!

53
00:04:15,522 --> 00:04:18,355
I'm in that final round tomorrow.

54
00:04:18,425 --> 00:04:21,451
Jeez, don't make come to get you.

55
00:04:23,230 --> 00:04:25,994
You're... in it?

56
00:04:29,870 --> 00:04:31,804
Please, Dad...

57
00:05:01,068 --> 00:05:02,330
Tomorrow, eh...

58
00:05:04,104 --> 00:05:05,002
Yeah.

59
00:05:17,017 --> 00:05:20,145
Tomorrow... is a full moon...

60
00:06:14,508 --> 00:06:17,136
To think you didn't even
get a scratch...

61
00:06:17,611 --> 00:06:19,442
Perfect, eh, Neji?

62
00:06:21,515 --> 00:06:23,949
That's enough warm up exercise...

63
00:06:25,819 --> 00:06:27,150
Shall we get going?

64
00:06:43,370 --> 00:06:47,101
<i>I was nervous and couldn't sleep.</i>

65
00:06:49,543 --> 00:06:53,206
<i>First...it's him...</i>
<i>in the first match.</i>

66
00:06:56,149 --> 00:07:00,176
<i>Quite honestly...even my Sharingan</i>
<i>can't see through his Tenketsu!</i>

67
00:07:00,854 --> 00:07:05,416
<i>The strongest man in the</i>
<i>Leaf is on my team.</i>

68
00:07:06,226 --> 00:07:09,423
<i>It is that...Neji Hyuga!</i>

69
00:07:09,496 --> 00:07:11,964
<i>Neji...Neji...Neji...</i>

70
00:07:38,225 --> 00:07:39,852
At last...

71
00:07:49,136 --> 00:07:51,502
The first match is Neji Hyuga, right?!

72
00:07:52,339 --> 00:07:55,069
Yeah. He's the number one rookie
from last year, right?!

73
00:07:55,142 --> 00:07:57,076
We can't miss the first match!

74
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:02,740
<i>Neji...Hyuga...</i>

75
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:10,416
Now I can summon a frog...
It'll be okay.

76
00:08:15,228 --> 00:08:19,289
<i>They all...Iook nasty.</i>

77
00:08:34,848 --> 00:08:35,712
Hinata!

78
00:08:36,116 --> 00:08:38,346
Ah! N-N-Naruto.

79
00:08:39,953 --> 00:08:41,887
W-What are you doing here?

80
00:08:42,289 --> 00:08:43,950
Today is the final round, isn't it?

81
00:08:46,693 --> 00:08:49,685
I... Just something...

82
00:08:50,831 --> 00:08:53,026
I came to check out this training field.

83
00:08:53,533 --> 00:08:56,764
This is the place where
I became Genin, so...

84
00:08:59,906 --> 00:09:02,704
Really? W-Why?

85
00:09:03,076 --> 00:09:07,206
N-Nothing... That doesn't matter!

86
00:09:08,048 --> 00:09:10,710
Y-You're right. I'm sorry.

87
00:09:13,487 --> 00:09:15,045
Say, Hinata...

88
00:09:15,722 --> 00:09:18,520
Neji's a relative of yours, right?

89
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:20,821
Y-Yes.

90
00:09:22,529 --> 00:09:24,793
Is he really strong...?

91
00:09:27,934 --> 00:09:28,730
Yes...

92
00:09:30,771 --> 00:09:31,738
I see.

93
00:09:32,139 --> 00:09:35,905
B-But you might be able to win, Naruto.

94
00:09:36,943 --> 00:09:39,707
Yeah. I'm strong, after all!

95
00:09:50,557 --> 00:09:52,957
I bet you can win, Naruto.

96
00:09:53,193 --> 00:09:53,989
What?

97
00:09:54,528 --> 00:09:55,620
You know...

98
00:09:55,929 --> 00:09:59,228
I... when you cheered for me,

99
00:09:59,533 --> 00:10:02,400
I felt like I was able to become
stronger than before.

100
00:10:02,869 --> 00:10:05,667
<i>Hinata! Hang tough!</i>

101
00:10:05,839 --> 00:10:07,397
When the preliminaries ended,

102
00:10:07,707 --> 00:10:10,301
I became able to like
myself just a little.

103
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,508
<i>I'll...</i>

104
00:10:16,650 --> 00:10:17,912
<i>stand...</i>

105
00:10:20,687 --> 00:10:22,348
<i>by my own...</i>

106
00:10:23,757 --> 00:10:24,917
<i>words.</i>

107
00:10:26,493 --> 00:10:30,259
<i>That is my way of Ninja.</i>

108
00:10:31,264 --> 00:10:35,291
From someone else's standpoint,
it might not look like anything's changed...

109
00:10:36,169 --> 00:10:39,730
but I feel like I was able to change.

110
00:10:41,108 --> 00:10:45,704
I've been thinking that it was...
thanks to you, Naruto.

111
00:10:48,482 --> 00:10:49,972
Say, Hinata...

112
00:10:51,284 --> 00:10:53,878
Did you really think so?

113
00:10:54,387 --> 00:10:54,978
What?

114
00:10:58,225 --> 00:11:02,184
I may look strong to you,

115
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:06,028
but all I do is mess up...

116
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:10,099
And I act tough because
I'm frustrated.

117
00:11:10,203 --> 00:11:11,693
It's not like that!

118
00:11:12,873 --> 00:11:15,273
Even when you messed up,

119
00:11:17,244 --> 00:11:21,271
in my view... you were always
a proud failure.

120
00:11:23,116 --> 00:11:27,712
W-When I look at you,
it impacts my heart.

121
00:11:28,889 --> 00:11:30,413
You're not perfect, so...

122
00:11:31,925 --> 00:11:32,892
So...

123
00:11:34,161 --> 00:11:35,628
It's because you mess up...

124
00:11:36,296 --> 00:11:39,288
that you have the strength
to rise up from that.

125
00:11:40,367 --> 00:11:45,464
I think such strength is
true strength.

126
00:11:47,674 --> 00:11:51,405
I... I think you're an
incredibly strong person.

127
00:12:01,087 --> 00:12:02,679
Thanks, Hinata!

128
00:12:05,625 --> 00:12:08,719
Even though I was always
the bottom one...

129
00:12:08,962 --> 00:12:11,556
I was tense in the shoulders, somehow!

130
00:12:12,132 --> 00:12:14,498
I was depressed,
which was totally not my character.

131
00:12:14,634 --> 00:12:17,262
But I feel better now!

132
00:12:18,438 --> 00:12:19,598
Naruto...

133
00:12:19,940 --> 00:12:22,704
Okay! I'm off to the match!

134
00:12:27,214 --> 00:12:28,272
Hinata...

135
00:12:28,648 --> 00:12:29,478
Huh?

136
00:12:30,183 --> 00:12:33,448
I kind of... thought you were...

137
00:12:33,954 --> 00:12:35,444
<i>W-What...?</i>

138
00:12:36,089 --> 00:12:39,456
...gloomy, hesitant and weird.

139
00:12:40,126 --> 00:12:41,388
Naruto...

140
00:12:42,429 --> 00:12:44,795
But I quite like... people...

141
00:12:47,133 --> 00:12:49,567
like you!

142
00:12:52,772 --> 00:12:54,069
<i>...like you!</i>

143
00:13:02,549 --> 00:13:07,282
Oh, yeah! Be sure to come watch me
kick that Neji's butt!

144
00:13:11,157 --> 00:13:14,251
Uh oh. Time to run!

145
00:13:14,628 --> 00:13:15,788
I-I'm late, late!

146
00:13:15,862 --> 00:13:18,126
See you later, Hinata!

147
00:13:22,969 --> 00:13:25,767
Sorry I'm late, Hinata.

148
00:13:26,306 --> 00:13:29,241
Well, Shino's match isn't until
quite a bit later, so...

149
00:13:29,843 --> 00:13:32,277
Hm? Hey? Hinata?

150
00:13:42,856 --> 00:13:45,552
Hmm? W-What?

151
00:13:54,868 --> 00:13:56,267
Oh, it's starting!

152
00:13:56,470 --> 00:13:58,267
Move, move!

153
00:13:58,572 --> 00:14:00,665
C'mon, move!

154
00:14:00,908 --> 00:14:03,342
Dang it! There's quite a distance!

155
00:14:03,410 --> 00:14:04,672
I won't make it!

156
00:14:05,212 --> 00:14:06,577
Brother Naruto!

157
00:14:10,217 --> 00:14:11,309
Konohamaru?!

158
00:14:12,252 --> 00:14:15,244
I've come to aid in brother's crisis, here!

159
00:14:15,455 --> 00:14:18,913
Konohamaru...
What're you doing here?!

160
00:14:18,992 --> 00:14:19,959
I'll tell you later!

161
00:14:20,160 --> 00:14:21,092
This way, here!

162
00:14:21,595 --> 00:14:25,827
There's an ace shortcut where
you can get straight to the arena, here!

163
00:14:26,366 --> 00:14:27,355
What?!

164
00:14:27,434 --> 00:14:30,301
All right!
Well done, Konohamaru!

165
00:14:30,637 --> 00:14:34,266
Those who control the
secret path control time.

166
00:14:34,508 --> 00:14:38,342
Oh, I see!
You're awesome, Konohamaru!

167
00:14:38,779 --> 00:14:41,612
As I recall, there's a hole
in the wall around here...

168
00:14:42,216 --> 00:14:42,875
Oh!

169
00:14:43,317 --> 00:14:44,147
Here it is!

170
00:14:46,019 --> 00:14:46,747
Oh!

171
00:14:47,921 --> 00:14:50,048
What's the matter, Konohamaru?

172
00:14:51,124 --> 00:14:53,957
The secret path has been repaired, here!

173
00:14:54,027 --> 00:14:55,392
Whaat...?

174
00:14:55,462 --> 00:14:57,987
Oh! There's no time!

175
00:14:58,265 --> 00:14:59,027
Brother!

176
00:14:59,566 --> 00:15:00,533
Next approach!

177
00:15:00,868 --> 00:15:03,632
Look! I'm <i>really</i> out of time.

178
00:15:06,106 --> 00:15:08,666
It's a secret, but there's
an awesome path

179
00:15:08,742 --> 00:15:11,939
that can get you inside the arena
in an instant, here!

180
00:15:12,379 --> 00:15:16,338
What?! All right!
Well done, Konohamaru!

181
00:15:18,886 --> 00:15:21,081
This hole is a shortcut?

182
00:15:21,455 --> 00:15:23,685
It's a straight shot to
the final round arena!

183
00:15:23,857 --> 00:15:25,449
No doubt, here!

184
00:15:25,626 --> 00:15:29,494
Straight shot, huh?
Okay!

185
00:15:29,897 --> 00:15:31,387
Let's hurry!

186
00:15:31,565 --> 00:15:32,429
Yeah!

187
00:15:37,838 --> 00:15:40,068
Konohamaru!
What's happening here?!

188
00:15:40,307 --> 00:15:41,569
It's okay, here!

189
00:15:41,642 --> 00:15:43,735
We're almost to the final
round arena, here!

190
00:15:44,611 --> 00:15:47,171
See? There's the exit, here!

191
00:15:47,247 --> 00:15:49,272
Oh, oh.

192
00:15:50,984 --> 00:15:51,916
What?!

193
00:15:59,993 --> 00:16:02,427
Hot-hot-hot-hot-hot-hot!

194
00:16:02,629 --> 00:16:06,895
T-This is... some kind of mistake!

195
00:16:08,201 --> 00:16:11,830
Kooonooohaaamaaaruuu!

196
00:16:12,239 --> 00:16:14,935
What the heck are you doing?!

197
00:16:15,509 --> 00:16:18,410
We've gotten further
and further away!

198
00:16:18,545 --> 00:16:20,342
Until just recently,

199
00:16:20,414 --> 00:16:22,939
it was connected to the
final round arena, here.

200
00:16:23,150 --> 00:16:25,482
Next approach, right away...

201
00:16:30,357 --> 00:16:31,346
This is it!

202
00:16:35,929 --> 00:16:39,922
If you ride this, you'll get to the
final round arena just like that, here!

203
00:16:41,902 --> 00:16:44,132
Huh? A bull?

204
00:16:44,438 --> 00:16:45,598
Think again, brother.

205
00:16:45,672 --> 00:16:50,439
A feudal lord Bull is not at all in
the same league as ordinary cows, here.

206
00:16:51,178 --> 00:16:54,045
Once they start running,
even race horses grow deathly pale.

207
00:16:54,114 --> 00:16:56,844
There's no way they can beat
a no nonsense feudal lord cow!

208
00:16:57,050 --> 00:16:59,280
Anyway, it's an awesome cow!

209
00:17:04,291 --> 00:17:07,488
Brother, if you leave the rest to this cow,

210
00:17:07,561 --> 00:17:10,029
it's just a short run to
the final round arena, here!

211
00:17:10,664 --> 00:17:12,291
Then, I'm counting on you.

212
00:17:12,532 --> 00:17:14,124
Okay, let's go!

213
00:17:19,573 --> 00:17:20,938
Huh? Wha...?!

214
00:17:25,846 --> 00:17:27,609
Ouch!

215
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:37,722
What?

216
00:17:51,671 --> 00:17:53,764
Brother, go for it, here!

217
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:56,900
Hey! Stop! Stop!

218
00:18:12,926 --> 00:18:16,589
<i>Hey hey, we're missing quite</i>
<i>a few people.</i>

219
00:18:17,531 --> 00:18:21,695
What's going on?
It's going to start.

220
00:18:22,569 --> 00:18:24,628
<i>What's the meaning of this?</i>
<i>Sasuke...?</i>

221
00:18:25,505 --> 00:18:27,063
<i>And even Naruto...</i>

222
00:18:34,214 --> 00:18:37,047
Why is it?!

223
00:18:45,025 --> 00:18:47,357
<i>This is bad!</i>

224
00:18:47,928 --> 00:18:48,860
That's it!

225
00:18:48,995 --> 00:18:50,758
Shadow Clone Jutsu!

226
00:18:53,467 --> 00:18:56,061
Guys! Scatter the rampaging cows!

227
00:18:56,136 --> 00:18:56,659
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

228
00:19:10,117 --> 00:19:14,315
What's wrong with you guys?
Why are you back, hey?!

229
00:19:15,122 --> 00:19:16,453
More appeared!

230
00:19:16,523 --> 00:19:18,650
The escape path was blocked!

231
00:19:18,758 --> 00:19:21,989
It won't do any good to multiply!

232
00:19:26,299 --> 00:19:27,732
Hmm? What the...?!

233
00:19:28,101 --> 00:19:29,500
Naruto Uzumaki?

234
00:19:29,769 --> 00:19:31,828
We leave the rest to you!

235
00:19:33,673 --> 00:19:35,538
Whoa, let us in, quick!

236
00:19:36,243 --> 00:19:36,766
Hey!

237
00:19:36,843 --> 00:19:38,401
Entry has already!

238
00:19:50,857 --> 00:19:53,849
<i>What kind...of entrance is</i>
<i>this kid making...?</i>

239
00:19:57,831 --> 00:19:59,162
Naruto.

240
00:19:59,299 --> 00:20:01,927
He's totally late.

241
00:20:03,470 --> 00:20:05,062
What a drag.

242
00:20:07,641 --> 00:20:12,772
Guys, run! A large herd of
stampeding bulls is coming.

243
00:20:13,079 --> 00:20:15,639
Huh? What are you talking about?

244
00:20:15,715 --> 00:20:19,549
Jeez! I'm serious.
So many of them...!

245
00:20:23,823 --> 00:20:26,519
Huh? Hey...
Where's Sasuke?

246
00:20:26,860 --> 00:20:29,658
The Dosu guy I'm supposed
to fight isn't here, either.

247
00:20:29,729 --> 00:20:31,492
Hey, you guys there.

248
00:20:31,665 --> 00:20:33,360
Don't be restless.

249
00:20:33,633 --> 00:20:37,000
Throw out your chests and
show your faces to the spectators!

250
00:20:58,024 --> 00:21:01,619
You guys are the stars of
this final round.

251
00:21:12,106 --> 00:21:15,473
<i>One! First, Tyson jumps and slamdunks</i>

252
00:21:15,543 --> 00:21:18,876
<i>Two! He kisses and hugs everyone</i>
<i>randomly and says "I LOVE YOU"</i>

253
00:21:18,947 --> 00:21:22,383
<i>Three! Masala masters Yoga</i>
<i>but hates curry</i>

254
00:21:22,444 --> 00:21:25,681
<i>Four! Sanchez is a lousy bullfighter. Ole!</i>

255
00:21:25,753 --> 00:21:32,124
<i>All over the world, the sky's smiling,</i>
<i>so look up and smile too</i>

256
